kBbwZ00?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2007:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band kick off the Magic Tour at the Hartford Civic Center with a set list that hews very closely to the rehearsal show.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Cx2NGZgmrVs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/PqjZw1zhUIM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4B9k1hobd-U?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/8F8tpuO6OKM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21561\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2007-10-02/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2007-10-02.jpg?fit=1950%2C1485&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1950,1485\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600873689&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2007-10-02\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2007-10-02.jpg?fit=758%2C577&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21561 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2007-10-02.jpg?resize=758%2C577&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"577\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2007-10-02.jpg?w=1950&amp;ssl=1 1950w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2007-10-02.jpg?resize=300%2C228&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2007-10-02.jpg?resize=1024%2C780&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2007-10-02.jpg?resize=768%2C585&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2007-10-02.jpg?resize=1536%2C1170&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2009:\u00a0</strong>On Night Two (of five) at Giants Stadium, Bruce plays the entire\u00a0<em>Darkness on the Edge of Town</em> album and still finds time to tour premiere &#8220;Jailhouse Rock&#8221; and &#8220;Long Walk Home&#8221; and give &#8220;Wrecking Ball&#8221; its second-ever appearance. Curt Ramm is present once again (as he will be for the remainder of the tour), and he, Ed Manion, Art Baron, and Larry Eagle form an almost-Sessions Band reunion during the &#8220;American Land&#8221; encore.</p>\n<div id=\"v-Z7igU6U2-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/Z7igU6U2?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-Wqc8dty3-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/Wqc8dty3?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allow